urbaani (film)|Qurbaani]]'' | Khadheeja | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="Qurbani" /> |- | 2000 !scope="row" | ''[[Ainbehge Loabi Firiehge Vaajib]]'' | Kuda Kaiydhaa Fulhu | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="ALFV" /> |- | 2000 !scope="row" | ''[[Hithu Vindhu]]'' | Kadhee | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="HithuVindhu" /> |- | 2000 !scope="row" | ''[[Ajaaib]]'' | Dhaleyka | | style="text-align: center;" |<ref name="Ajaaib" /> |- | 2000 !scope="row" | ''[[Majubooru Loabi]]'' | Sheela | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="sihthi" /> |- | 2003 !scope="row"|''[[Edhi Edhi Hoadheemey]]'' | Herself | Special appearance | style="text-align: center;"| <ref name=EEHReview>{{cite web|url=http://www.haveeru.com.mv/entertainment/2114 | title=Edhi Edhi Hoadheemey ‚Äì a film some moviegoers may desperately seek |publisher=Haveeru |date=14 September 2003 |accessdate=3 March 2012 | url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130219030743/http://www.haveeru.com.mv/entertainment/2114 |archivedate=19 February 2013| df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- | 2003 !scope="row" | ''[[Vehey Vaarey Therein]]'' | Sorcerer | Special appearance | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="VeheyVaarey" /> |- |}
